726738f-a.title: Queens: Furmanville Avenue - 82nd Place
726738f-a.text:
Furmanville Avenue, at 82nd Place, viewing southwest-
ward toward Dry Harbor Road (telephone poles) and Juniper
Valley Road and showing a path across the empty lots,
evidently a pedestrians' shortcut between Furmanville Avenue
and the latter points.
July 1, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
